    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Humans vs Gorilla is a simulation game with goal being answering the million dollar question. Who would win in a fight? 100 Humans, or 1 Gorilla. <br>In this simulated battle, you use the sheer indomitable human spirit, to try to fight an enemy player gorilla. With 100 friends, and 1 unlucky foe, you will live and answer the question we have been asking for eternity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features : <br>Gorilla <br>100 Humans </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're not sold on this game yet, just listen to what our very satisfied customers have to say about it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360940/extras/7e44217c4d4213dd9ae0fb8a831547e2.avif?t=1770245338\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hrrrmmph... hooOOH hoo hoo HAAAH!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>THUMP THUMP—</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WRAAAAH! GRRRRUH huh huh huh—THWUMP!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>BWOOM bwoom bwoom...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360940/extras/17d05e5ba743a7c20bd30724fea14284.avif?t=1770245338\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 out of 100 Players recommend 100 Humans vs Gorilla to their friends!<br>It's either the last standing player, or the Gorilla himself.</p>",
